data.description: Complete Remodel in 2006 on this Beautiful Rural Eagle Point Home. Amazing master suite with separate sitting areas. Panoramic view of Mt. McLoughlin. Large master bath with separate tub and shower, coffered ceilings and tile flooring. Open plan in the living area and Granite kitchen counters. Covered porch that runs across the front of the house. The oversized garage with extra living is 720 sq.ft. The driveway is stamped concrete with lots of parking areas. The back yard patio area is very private and has a nice water feature. Nice place to relax. RV parking and hook ups. Whole house water filtration system. Carpets freshly shampooed. Will work with buyers agent. Please contact owner at 541-200-4079 to schedule showing.
